sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant WAL as PostgreSQL WAL
    participant JVec as JVector Index
    participant Disk as Disk Snapshot

    Note over App,Disk: NORMAL OPERATION - Write Path

    App->>WAL: 1. INSERT vector_embedding (indexed=false)
    WAL-->>App: Committed (durable)
    App->>JVec: 2. addGraphNode()
    JVec-->>App: Added to in-memory index
    App->>WAL: 3. UPDATE indexed=true

    Note over JVec,Disk: PERIODIC SNAPSHOT (every 5 min)

    JVec->>Disk: Write HNSW graph to disk
    Disk-->>JVec: Snapshot complete

    Note over App,Disk: CRASH SCENARIO

    App-xApp: JVM Crash / Kill -9

    Note over App,Disk: RECOVERY ON RESTART

    App->>Disk: 1. Load last snapshot
    Disk-->>JVec: HNSW graph loaded
    App->>WAL: 2. SELECT WHERE indexed=false
    WAL-->>App: Unindexed entries

    loop Replay WAL
        App->>JVec: addGraphNode()
        App->>WAL: UPDATE indexed=true
    end

    App->>App: Ready to serve requests

